Souvenir Figure Set', 'gi-joe', 'Original', 2013, 62, 5, 'Cobra Mortal, S.A.W.-Viper (x2), Spearhead, Repeater, Charbroil', 'Nocturnal Fire was a theme of exclusive souvenirs available at the 2013 "GIJoeCon" official G.I. Joe convention, including the Nocturnal Fire Kreon Souvenir Figure Set, and the individually-packaged Kreon Hit & Run. The theme is based on the G.I. Joe nocturnal operations sub-team Night Force battling a Cobra demolitions team led by the Venezuelan warlord Cobra Mortal.

Unlike the rounded shoulders typical of human Kreons in other sub-lines (including G.I. Joe Kreons), the kreons made available as part of this theme feature the angular shoulder style used for Transformers Kreons.', NULL, 'micro_changer', NULL, 'gi-joe/wk4900.jpg', NULL, NULL, 'https://kreo.fandom.com/wiki/Nocturnal%20Fire', 'https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/kreo/images/7/73/Nocturnal_fire_poster.jpg/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/800?cb=20140110161411', '2026-03-01 08:09:04.927425'::timestamp, '2026-03-01 09:36:27.990073'::timestamp) ON CONFLICT (set_number) DO UPDATE SET name = EXCLUDED.name, franchise = EXCLUDED.franchise, sub_line = EXCLUDED.sub_line, year = EXCLUDED.year, piece_count = EXCLUDED.piece_count, kreons_count = EXCLUDED.kreons_count, kreons_included = EXCLUDED.kreons_included, description = EXCLUDED.description, price_retail = EXCLUDED.price_retail, product_type = EXCLUDED.product_type, image_url = EXCLUDED.image_url, image_path = EXCLUDED.image_path, pdf_url = EXCLUDED.pdf_url, pdf_path = EXCLUDED.pdf_path, wiki_url = EXCLUDED.wiki_url, wiki_image_url = EXCLUDED.wiki_image_url, updated_at = EXCLUDED.updated_at;
