thumb

The Decepticon Ambush set features Cliffjumper busting through a Decepticon checkpoint and comes included with three Vehicon Kreons. While each one uses the same base body and tampographs, each one is slightly different from the others; one comes with wheels on his legs, another has a Shockwave wrist-mounted blaster, and one has [[Wheeljack (Kre-O)|', NULL, 'micro_changer', NULL, 'transformers/wk2339.jpg', NULL, 'pdfs/WK2339_instructions_scan.pdf', 'https://kreo.fandom.com/wiki/Vehicon', 'https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/kreo/images/7/72/Decepticon-Ambush-Kreon-Vehicon-2_1350921950.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20130220044516', '2026-03-01 08:12:24.535051'::timestamp, '2026-03-01 10:31:16.001642'::timestamp) ON CONFLICT (set_number) DO UPDATE SET name = EXCLUDED.name, franchise = EXCLUDED.franchise, sub_line = EXCLUDED.sub_line, year = EXCLUDED.year, piece_count = EXCLUDED.piece_count, kreons_count = EXCLUDED.kreons_count, kreons_included = EXCLUDED.kreons_included, description = EXCLUDED.description, price_retail = EXCLUDED.price_retail, product_type = EXCLUDED.product_type, image_url = EXCLUDED.image_url, image_path = EXCLUDED.image_path, pdf_url = EXCLUDED.pdf_url, pdf_path = EXCLUDED.pdf_path, wiki_url = EXCLUDED.wiki_url, wiki_image_url = EXCLUDED.wiki_image_url, updated_at = EXCLUDED.updated_at;
INSERT INTO kreo_products (set_number, name, franchise, sub_line, year, piece_count, kreons_count, kreons_included, description, price_retail, product_type, image_url, image_path, pdf_url, pdf_path, wiki_url, wiki_image_url, discovered_at, updated_at) VALUES ('WK5495', 'Wheeljack', 'transformers', 'Quest for Energon', 2012, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'thumb Wheeljack is a Kreon included in the Street Showdown building set.
Ah! Welcome to my lab! Don’t touch anything! Everything in here is top secret, and probably explosive. My job is to help the AUTOBOTS track down ENERGON before the DECEPTICONS do, and while I usually focus my research on things that melt or detonate, ENERGON-tracking is interesting too. I guess.

Favorite Creation:
GRIMLOCK.

Favorite Tool:
Quantum Circuit Bender.

Best Friend:
AUTOBOT RATCHET repairs me whenever I blow parts off.



Character Profile:

You won''t find a more committed Autobot than Wheeljack. He''s been dreaming up new and awesome weapons to use against the Decepticons. He''s famous for creating the Quantum Circuit Breaker, but don''t mention it around Ratchet because he''ll get jealous.', NULL, 'building_set', NULL, 'transformers/wk5495.jpg', NULL, NULL, 'https://kreo.fandom.com/wiki/Wheeljack', 'https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/kreo/images/b/b3/Wheeljack_1339101179.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20130309061633', '2026-03-01 08:12:26.446726'::timestamp, '2026-03-01 09:35:22.677282'::timestamp) ON CONFLICT (set_number) DO UPDATE SET name = EXCLUDED.name, franchise = EXCLUDED.franchise, sub_line = EXCLUDED.sub_line, year = EXCLUDED.year, piece_count = EXCLUDED.piece_count, kreons_count = EXCLUDED.kreons_count, kreons_included = EXCLUDED.kreons_included, description = EXCLUDED.description, price_retail = EXCLUDED.price_retail, product_type = EXCLUDED.product_type, image_url = EXCLUDED.image_url, image_path = EXCLUDED.image_path, pdf_url = EXCLUDED.pdf_url, pdf_path = EXCLUDED.pdf_path, wiki_url = EXCLUDED.wiki_url, wiki_image_url = EXCLUDED.wiki_image_url, updated_at = EXCLUDED.updated_at;
